  <eligibility>
    <inclusivecriteria>-  Type 1 diabetes

          -  Current treatment with any insulin in any regimen

          -  Body mass index (BMI) below 38.0 kg/m2

          -  HbA1c below or equal to 13.0%</inclusivecriteria>
    <inclusiveminage>18</inclusiveminage>
    <inclusiveminagetype>Years</inclusiveminagetype>
