    <inclusivegender>Both males and females</inclusivegender>
    <healthyvolunteer>No</healthyvolunteer>
    <exclusivecriteria>-  Total daily insulin dosage more than 100 IU/day

          -  Current acute or chronic pulmonary disease (excluding asthma)

          -  Recurrent major hypoglycaemia

          -  Proliferative retinopathy or maculopathy requiring acute treatment

          -  Smoker

          -  Chest X-ray with clinically significant abnormalities</exclusivecriteria>
